            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I attended my son's Annual day. It was an amazing experience. Every performance was and outstanding one. I was completely into it. There zeal, there efforts were spot on. The theme \"Yugantar\" was very well thought and beautifully presented by all the super talented kids. Ofcource it wasn't possible without all the attention, efforts and guidance of the all the hardworking teachers and the management. Creativity at its best! proud to be part of the lotusian family. Each and every minutest bit of the event was fabulous 👌.  I feel at ease with the thought that my son is in one of the best schools of Noida. He is getting the best possible academic learning and is in a well protected environment.  👏 👏 👏",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
