            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My kids are in Lotus valley international school.\nI am amazed with all the love hardwork and cooperation of teachers peer group and support of principle mam in all aspects . Recently attended the annual function on 1st Feb 2024 theme named yugaantar...\nThe show was so fabulous enchanting and mesimerising..\nThe hard work made by kids and teachers has paid off .\nThe live performance I witnessed this year was not less than Sanjay Leela bansali movie...\nReally didn't want it to get over ...\nEverything was just perfect costume colors music props hats off to all .\nLvis rocks!!!!\nThnkuu so much ...",
          "publisher": {
