            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Just attended the middle school annual function titled Yugantar on 31st Jan 2024. Fabulously choreographed and managed by the teachers and school staffs. Kids performed brilliantly. I loved the theme in which great emphasis were give to our culture and traditional values... Hats off to LVIS, Noida for such concept and meticulous execution by all the students.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
