          "reviewBody": "My grand son is in Lotus valley from 2016. My experience with Lotus valley school is fabulous. Each and every day I am expecting more and more and school is giving more than it. It's really hard work of teachers, parents and students. We are always feeling a strong bond with school as a family.",
