            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The Annual function of the middle wing,'Yugaantar' was a spectacular show. The theme of the show knowing about our country's rich heritage and culture at this age is a need of time. And the way all the students presented it was amazing. Hats off to the entire team of Lotus Valley International school, Noida.",
