          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Witnessed the annual day extravaganza of the Middle school classes at Lotus Valley, Noida. Wonderfully planned and played out acts that focussed not just on India's rich , ancient culture & heritage but also on the leadership role that our country is all set to take up internationally & how our young generation is being prepared to marry the past with the future & contribute towards India's surge as VishwaGuru. LVIS is doing a great job in preparing our children for the challenges and opportunities of today & tomorrow.",
